data.meta_description: 6 likes, 0 comments - astoriafilmfestival on June 4, 2024: "At the Astoria Film Festival Media Education Panel on June 1 during the festival, Adam Brier EdD, Deputy Executive Director of CTE at New York City Public Schools talked about the importance of CTE Education at schools like @actvf_hs @artanddesignnyc and @motionpicturenyc in supporting career development and opportunities for students to pursue media production jobs.".
